{
  "stem": "6878.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was fantastic, how they handled us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from there, we crossed into Salzburg, from Linz to Salzburg by train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Salzburg, we were four months in a camp, in an American Zone camp, and from there we went on near the border, which it was Seefeld.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the Zionist organization organized for kids-- Selwyn was then a little bit bigger-- for kids to go on holiday.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Selwyn was already 2 and 1/2.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were about 150 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no work to be done.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We lived on-- on money given to us from the Zionist Federation or from where.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wasn't working, not even one day there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the main objective was to go to--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then from Salzburg, the group went off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The woman in charge of the kids, of her kids, every woman had 10 kids.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she wouldn't take Selwyn because he was too small, so I gave her a $10 note.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was kosher, and she took him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were because when the train went off, we don't know where they go, when they go.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they taking him-- they take him across the border, and one day, we will go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So Ida fainted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On the Salzburg station, she fainted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There we lost a little kid, and here, we're letting go a little boy which we don't know whether we'll see him ever again and so on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she fainted on the Salzburg station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, I revived Ida.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Ida, come.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- and I took her back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And from there, we crossed the-- the Alps.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
